Real Madrid face Atletico Madrid in the Champions League semi-final on Tuesday night . 
  Carlo Ancelotti must accommodate Cristiano Ronaldo, Gareth Bale and Karim Benzema in a 4-3-3  . 
  Diego Simeone will flood the midfield with Arda Turan and Koke . 
  The Madrid derby is the greatest city derby in world football . 
  Real and Atletico have met six times in European competition . 
 